# Context filter for packages/server/Dockerfile (BuildKit honors <dockerfile>.dockerignore).
# The build context is the repo root; keep it lean — node_modules and build outputs are recreated
# inside the image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.vite
**/.turbo
.git
.github
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
data
packages/*/data
